name: 桑默·乔伊·坎贝尔
name_full: 桑默·乔伊·坎贝尔 Summer Joy Campbell
introduction: Summer Joy Campbell is an actress who found her passion for acting in her high school theater program and began her on-screen acting career in 2016. Her most recent works include Bottoms, Queen Sugar and Paradise Lost. Summer is a multi-passionate individual and when she is not acting, she can be found pursuing other creative endeavors such as painting, baking, and photography.
